<Desc><entry>Aims to assist people with disabilities and long-term health conditions into real employment through providing training and assistance to people searching for work in the local area and through employing people directly in the Remploy factory.  The Remploy factory manufactures educational and office furniture which is sold to schools and colleges throughout the UK and offers a packing service to a number of companies.  Also provides development tailored to suit individual needs in areas of CV writing, interviewing skills and many more.  Remploy is a not-for-profit company.</entry>
